    # ── Style Metrics ────────────────────────────────────────────
    narr:StyleMetrics_PerspectiveResponseOrdering a narr:StyleMetrics ;
      skos:broader narr:StyleMetrics ;

      narr:AverageSentenceLength "22"^^xsd:integer ;
      narr:ActiveVoiceRatio "0.82"^^xsd:decimal ;
      narr:JargonDensity "0.18"^^xsd:decimal ;
      skos:note "Technical-architectural register. Active voice dominant in editorial sections; passive used sparingly for design decisions ('was retired', 'is now ordered'). Jargon density moderate — engineering terms (byte-stable, cache_control, cache-hostile, per-call) used without definition, implying internal/technical audience. Numbered lists for the four-section structure. Blockquote for verbatim speaker attribution. Sentence length varies: short declaratives at decision peaks ('Focus selects what to append, never what to move.') vs. longer analytical sentences for the honesty bound." .

